      "summary": "We are currently collaborating with our first group of beta users to refine our product and find the right fit for the market. If you're interested in shaping the future of Tamias and becoming an early adopter, feel free to join our community. There's no obligation to contribute, and we're thrilled that you want to try out the system.",
      "image": "/images/plan.png",
      "tag": "Update"
